Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:03.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:06.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what this recap tastes like!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:07.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too damn suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We headed off to Tenroujima
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:11.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,for the S Class Advancement Exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:13.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but began to suspect that \NMest, one of the participants,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:15.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't actually a member of the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:16.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He is far too suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:20.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But approaching the island \Nwas an even greater danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know this danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:25.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just way too damn suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:04.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref alive, and on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:10.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And to think that Master Hades of Grimoire \NHeart and his personal guard are coming here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:14.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He called them the Seven Kin \Nof Purgatory, if I recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:17.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And he said that one of them was \Nalready here on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:20.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a good situation. \NAt any rate, we must hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:23.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll search for Wendy and \NMest, then return to the camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:40.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are the two of \Nyou doing all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:42.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You, stay quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:44.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:46.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:53.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect you're a wizard whose magic \Ncan manipulate people's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:03:01.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You cast a spell on the members of the \Nguild, making them think you were a member.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:08.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about Mystogan, everything \Nseems completely out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:11.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of anyone else \Nyou have any connection to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:17.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And furthermore, to not know the \Nmeaning of the guild's signal flare...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:19.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to talk \Nyour way out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:31.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's teleportation magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:32.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:34.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mest-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:38.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:43.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Makarov's Charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:03:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:16.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He... protected Wendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you? Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well seeing through me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:39.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a person coming from the tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:40.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Azuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:47.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am one of Grimoire Heart's \NSeven Kin of Purgatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimoire Heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:50.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Dark Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:55.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So the signal flare before was \Nto warn of incoming enemy attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just say you've realized far too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:03.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What... in blazes is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:08.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if I snuck onto \NFairy Tail's holy ground
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:12.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would find a skeleton \Nor two in their closet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:21.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Black Wizard Zeref and Grimoire \NHeart's Lady luck is with me for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:23.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who {\i1}are{\i0} you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:27.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't realized yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from the Magic Council!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:34.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I infiltrated Fairy Tail to find \Ndirty secrets to destroy you with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:36.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Council?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:39.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:42.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that's come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:47.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the impossible to find \NGrimoire Heart coming here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I finish you off here, that \Npromotion will be more than a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:57.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I was right \Nto station warships of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:06:01.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the Magic Council's Enforcement and \NDetention Corps nearby just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:06.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll round you all up! I'll \Ncrush all you devils' hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warships?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about those?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:22.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let us start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:33.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it acceptable for me to \Nbegin my job now, Mr. Official?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:47.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A red signal flare... Signifying \Nan incoming enemy attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What have things come to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mavis...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:58.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail's founding \Nmaster, Mavis Vermillion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:03.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have led the enemy here to \NFairy Tail's holy grounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:07.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How far have I failed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:10.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all my responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:13.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I will accept the \Npunishment for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:18.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So therefore... at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:20.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...protect the young ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:28.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard like, a big \Nexplosion from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the enemy here already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:32.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:33.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:45.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ships all exploded in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:52.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Council's warships... \NLike they were nothing at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:02.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,BLEVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:28.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I only had a sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:31.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will support you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:35.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O swift wind that dashes through the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:39.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vernier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's gotten lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:45.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O strength of arm to cleave the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:51.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what they call Support Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:53.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can dodge this explosion magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mest-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an official of the Magic Council!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:18.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:21.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please lend me your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:26.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to destroy your \Nguild so I could be promoted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:30.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there's no way we'll be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:37.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:42.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My explosions will reach you, \Nno matter how far you run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:45.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A point-blank...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:50.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminating this guy first is the smart move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Sky Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:57.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tower Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:19.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:21.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A tower of flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:24.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one in the guild can use magic like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've hit my limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:56.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Seven Kin of \NPurgatory I've heard rumors of?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this guild just filled with \Ncats and children, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:07.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are six more of these guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:12.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way... for Fairy Tail to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:25.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where's the meeting point again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a portable base.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:32.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Going through these ruins is a short cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we doing this when we \Nshould be searching for a grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:40.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is ridiculous! Why'd \Nthis have to happen {\i1}now{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:41.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:47.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Gajeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:51.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry back, or \Nthey're going to show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's split up right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:59.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in big trouble if \Nthey attack as we are now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:24.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear-san, you're more into this than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:27.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. To me as well, this is a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:31.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go... To the Eden known as battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:36.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A-And me... Me, too, I'll... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:43.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Ul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go being so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:50.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What's wrong, Meldy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fairy's Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You kiddin' me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:32.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Big...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Makarov...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:45.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,736...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:48.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,48 years earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:54.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, be the 3rd master of Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:59.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I ain't cut out for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:01.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You, my boy, can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already 40!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:08.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You love your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:12.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a human who can believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:15.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure you will lead a wonderful guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:23.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Mavis to me, and now \Nfrom me to you, Makarov...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:30.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I entrust the future of Fairy Tail to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:35.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not pass any further! {YOU SHALL NOT PASS}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Large explosion on the right side!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He shredded our reinforced \Narmor like nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:56.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:01.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Increase speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:10.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Beam Cannon, Jupiter...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:37.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:38.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This{\i0} is Makarov?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:41.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:45.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Ark...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Restore...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:01.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Caprico, take everyone to the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:03.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Master Hades?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:07.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall deal with Makarov.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:08.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:22.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It matters not where you run to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:40.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As is Fairy Tail tradition, I shall count \Nto three before rendering judgment upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:49.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The super magic which affects only those \Nwhom the caster views as enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:51.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:54.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Law, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:02.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, get yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:06.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily, Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:08.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the two of you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:10.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:12.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Someone did this to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:20.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:30.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My memory manipulation magic's worn off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:35.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Explanation:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:41.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Memory Manipulation is magic which enables \Nyou to alter other people's memories of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:47.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, like charms, if your \Nreal identity is revealed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:50.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the magic is lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:54.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san... He's a person \Nfrom the Magic Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:57.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice coat you have there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:02.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... The enemy is the Magic Council?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:04.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayiaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:05.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is Grimoire Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:09.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Dark Guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:10.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimoire Heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:14.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they one of the three corners \Nof the Dark Guild Baram Alliance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:18.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:20.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People are coming from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:52.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather forecast didn't \Nsay anything about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up, give me a break here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:58.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those all humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:21.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're already here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:29.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Man, I will not allow trespassers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:31.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:38.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These numbers are nothing to scoff at.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:40.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still coming down from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:10.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my... Here comes the noisy bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:21.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I present to you this Fairy sacrifice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:36.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can meet at last... Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:46.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the start of another war?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:57.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:59.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:04.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:07.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:20.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimoire Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This magic is a deterrent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:28.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not cast it recklessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:31.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you refuse to back down,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:36.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then together we shall reach the \Nultimate of unfortunate ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:41.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:43.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am heading on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:50.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make this guild one to be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:52.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:54.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:22:01.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the master now, Makarov.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:07.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a while, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:11.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master... Purehito...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.64,0:23:58.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, do you know about Lost Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.21,0:24:00.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loh-st...? Like, as in chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.84,0:24:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's roast chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.74,0:24:04.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost, not roast!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.41,0:24:06.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It means magic that's \Ndisappeared into history!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.40,0:24:08.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck did you get chicken from?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.33,0:24:11.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic ain't gonna disappear! \NThis isn't Edolas, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm trying to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.23,0:24:16.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Lost Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.72,0:24:19.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, I'm tired out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.15,0:24:21.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you tired when we \Nhaven't done anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.38,0:24:24.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because I have to deal with you!
